<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/nl.43.50430>
    bibo:endPage "166" ;
    bibo:journal "Nota Lepidopterologica" ;
    bibo:startPage "151" ;
    bibo:volume "43" ;
    dc:creator "Corley, Martin F. V.; Rosete, Jorge; Ferreira, Sonia" ;
    dc:date "2020" ;
    dc:title "Mondeguina, a new genus for Apatetris mediterranella Nel & Varenne, 2012, with description of a new species from Portugal (Lepidoptera, Gelechiidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/nl.43.50430.figures2-3>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/nl.43.50430.figures4-5>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/nl.43.50430.figure6>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/nl.43.50430.figures7-8>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/nl.43.50430.figures9-10>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/nl.43.50430.figure11>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/nl.43.50430.figure1> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/nl.43.50430.figures2-3>
    dc:description "Figures 2, 3. Habitus. 2. Mondeguina atlanticella male, Portugal, Ilha da Morraceira (A. Lameirinhas). 3. M. atlanticella female, Portugal, Ilha da Morraceira (A. Lameirinhas)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/414702" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/nl.43.50430.figures4-5>
    dc:description "Figures 4, 5. Male genitalia. 4. Mondeguina atlanticella, Portugal, Ilha da Morraceira (P. Huemer 19 / 1230). 5. M. mediterranella, Italy, Canale Quarantia (P. Huemer 05 / 1230)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/414703" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/nl.43.50430.figure6>
    dc:description "Figure 6. Male genitalia. Mondeguina atlanticella, Portugal, Ilha da Morraceira (M. Dale 02492)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/414704" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/nl.43.50430.figures7-8>
    dc:description "Figures 7, 8. Female genitalia. 7. Mondeguina atlanticella, Portugal, Ilha da Morraceira (M. Dale 02484). 8. M. mediterranella, France, Arles (M. Dale 02653)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/414705" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/nl.43.50430.figures9-10>
    dc:description "Figures 9, 10. Habitat of Mondeguina atlanticella at Ilha da Morraceira (J. Rosete)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/414706" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/nl.43.50430.figure11>
    dc:description "Figure 11. Distribution of Mondeguina species. Red circles Mondeguina atlanticella. Yellow circles Mondeguina mediterranella." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/414707" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/nl.43.50430.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Gene tree obtained by Maximum Likelihood (ML) analysis of five Mondeguina gen. nov. specimens within the context of representative sequences of close related genera: Apatetris, Catatinagma, Dactylotula and Epiphthora based on available sequences of a fragment of cytochrome c oxidase I gene (COI) (658 bp). Bootstrap values (> 90 %) are indicated at nodes." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/414701" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

